      "EvilAuraPassiveAKingArthurEvilBoss": {
        "id": "EvilAuraPassiveAKingArthurEvilBoss",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Returned King",
          "description": "If this unit would be defeated, it instead survives with 1 HP and then cannot be defeated until its next turn. This effect can trigger only once each time this unit enters the battlefield, and is considered a Hold Ground+ effect.\n\nEach time this unit takes damage from an attack and survives until after the end of the turn with more than 1 HP, this unit will immediately get the turn by having its TU reduced to 0. This extra turn may be interrupted by other effects that influence the turn order (e.g. other stuns targeting the lowest TU target). This is not considered a Counter Skin type effect. This effect cannot trigger again until 50TU advances.\n\nThis unit enters battle with 1% HP Regen for 100TU. A unit with 1% HP Regen will heal for 1% of their max HP after every turn. HP Regen effects will overwrite existing HP Regen effects."
        }
